Glovo is the #1 app for ordering anything you want! With more than 240,000 restaurants & stores available, and delivery in minutes. Download the app now & order a Glovo!

Easily order food, groceries and gifts in your city without leaving home.

Want to order food straight to your door? Or get a grocery delivery of your essentials? We save you time, when you don’t have it. 

WHY USE GLOVO?

▶ Over 80 million downloads worldwide.
▶ Order in 23 countries including Spain, Portugal, Romania, Morocco, Italy, Poland, Croatia, Ukraine, Georgia, Kazakhstan, Kyrgyzstan, Tunisia, Kenya, Uganda, Ivory Coast, Nigeria, Bulgaria, Serbia, Armenia, Bosnia-herzegovina, Montenegro, Moldova & Andorra.
▶ More than 240,000 restaurants, supermarkets and stores available globally.
▶ Deliveries from the biggest chains: McDonald's, Burger King, KFC, Pizza Hut, Taco Bell, Telepizza, Starbucks, Domino’s Pizza, Carrefour, PENNY., Eataly, Flying Tiger, Kiko Milano, Lafarmacia, Auchan, Decathlon, MediaMarkt and many more.
▶ Your favourite food delivery in minutes: Order burgers, pizza, chicken, kebab, pasta, sandwiches, sushi, poké…anything you want.
▶ Pay however you like. We accept PayPal, card payment, cash and even restaurant vouchers.
▶ Track your delivery or takeaway in real time and chat with our support team if need be.
▶ Subscribe to Glovo Prime and get unlimited free deliveries of food, groceries, and shopping. Save on every delivery! Available in selected countries.
▶ Invite your friends and earn money for each one who places an order on the app.

YOUR FAVOURITE FOOD, IN MINUTES!

Fancy a tasty dinner? Has it been a long day? You deserve to have your food delivered to your door! Or are you on your way somewhere? You can order food to take away and grab it on the go.

With Glovo, you can order up to 65 different types of food in your city. Including a burger from the most famous restaurants, to ordering from your favourite sushi place. There are more than 216,000 restaurants available worldwide for delivery or takeaway of your favourite food, in a matter of minutes.


GROCERY DELIVERY WITHOUT LEAVING HOME

Forget something from the supermarket? Got friends over and want to order another round of drinks or snacks? 

Now you can also order your groceries from the supermarket. Choose whatever you want from your favourite supermarket or local store and Glovo will deliver it to you in a few minutes. Food, snacks, drinks, something sweet, a missing ingredient... any groceries you need! 


THE APP TO ORDER ANYTHING

Glovo delivers everything. Find more than 27000 stores on the app, with all kinds of products. All your shopping on one app: surprise gifts, a last-minute purchase or whatever you need.

And if you need to send or pick up something in your city, Glovo can run errands for you. Choose a pick-up and delivery point and a courier will take care of the rest, with delivery in minutes!


NEED HELP? CONTACT US

If you’re looking for help with an order or have any questions about Glovo, please contact our support team via the support section in our app or on our website.

You can also find us on:
▶ Our site: https://glovoapp.com/ 
▶ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/glovoappES 
▶ Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/glovo_es/ 
▶ Twitter: https://twitter.com/Glovo_ES

Download Glovo now! Order food, groceries, shopping or courier service - with delivery in minutes.

kkal ai is the intelligent food diary that transforms calorie counting into a quick, effortless experience tailored for the UK. Forget the old-fashioned method of pen-and-paper logging—simply snap a photo of your meal and let our advanced AI instantly determine calories, protein, carbohydrates, fats, and essential nutrients. Designed with modern British lifestyles in mind, kkal ai streamlines nutrition tracking whether you’re following a slimming plan, building lean muscle, or striving for healthier eating.

Key Features:
• Smart Photo Logging: Take a quick snap of your plate and let the AI accurately identify your meal and calculate its nutritional content. Enjoy hassle-free logging that saves you valuable time.
• Detailed Macro Breakdown: Instantly receive a comprehensive overview of proteins, carbs, fats, fibre, sugars, and more—so you always know what you’re consuming.
• Barcode Scanning for UK Products: Easily scan packaged foods from Tesco, Sainsbury’s, Aldi, and other local retailers to automatically add detailed nutritional data.
• Customised Goal Setting & Real-Time Feedback: Set tailored targets for weight loss, muscle building, or maintenance, and receive progress reports and insights that keep you motivated.
• Intuitive User Interface: Navigate a clean, user-friendly design that makes reviewing your food log and tracking progress a breeze, perfect for both newcomers and seasoned users.
• Privacy First: No registration required—start using kkal ai immediately with the assurance that your data is kept safe and secure.
• Offline Tracking: Log your meals on the go, even without an internet connection. Your data syncs automatically when you’re back online.

Built specifically for the UK market, kkal ai features an extensive food database that includes British favourites, popular pub meals, and local retail products. Our system recognises traditional portion sizes and measurements (grams, millilitres), ensuring every meal is captured accurately. Users have praised kkal ai for its simplicity and precision. One delighted user stated, “Finally, an app that truly understands UK portions and products—it’s made my healthy eating journey so much easier!”

Whether you’re part of a formal programme like Slimming World or simply in need of a reliable, private food diary, kkal ai delivers a fast, intelligent solution that adapts to your lifestyle. Download kkal ai today and experience the convenience of smart food tracking—your modern, no-fuss calorie counter designed for everyday life in the UK.

Take control of your nutrition, make informed dietary decisions, and join the growing community of users who have embraced a simpler way to log meals. Your journey towards a healthier, balanced life begins with kkal ai.

With 97+ billion matches to date, Tinder® is the top free dating app and the best place to meet new people, with safety features that work to help you date more safely. Looking for love? An open relationship? Trying to find a date or new friends to chat with? Connect with local people everywhere on Tinder and get the best out of your dating experience:

Come As You Are: whether you're straight, gay, bisexual or anything in between, you can be who you are and find who you want on Tinder.
Date Beyond Photos: share your interests and learn more about your matches to get the conversation started.
Seek What You’re Looking For: set your relationship goals and make connections on your terms.

HOW TINDER WORKS
It’s easy and fun to find new people on Tinder®. Express yourself to make your personality shine in your profile and stand out to potential matches. Answer a prompt, share a little about you and show your face in your pics to increase your match-making potential. Use the Swipe Right™ feature to like and the Swipe Left™ feature to nope. If they like you back, It’s a Match! And with our double opt-in feature, it’s only a match if the interest is mutual.

PUT SAFETY FIRST
Try some of our safety features to help you make connections more confidently:

– Share My Date: share date plans with friends and fam, so they know who you’re planning to meet up with and where
– Get Photo Verified: verify your photos to help potential matches know it’s really you in that cute pic & increase your chances of matching
– Are You Sure / Does This Bother You: Tinder detects inappropriate language so people think twice before sending a disrespectful message
– Report a Profile: quickly report and block profiles with suspicious activity or inappropriate behaviour
– Block Contacts: take control and block anyone (like an ex) you don’t want to see on the app
– Video Chat: hitting it off in chat? Test your online dating chemistry and meet new people from home!

TRY TINDER PLUS
– Unlimited likes for you to catch feelings for as many new people as you want
– Use Passport Mode™ to match and chat with locals anywhere in the world before you arrive
– Unlimited Rewinds to undo your last like or nope
– Go Incognito and be seen only by the people you like

EXPERIENCE TINDER GOLD
– Get everything in Tinder Plus™, and try it out for a week before you commit to a monthly subscription
– See who likes you and match with them on the spot for faster connections
– Monthly Boost puts your profile to the top for 30 minutes to help increase your profile views
– Weekly Super Likes, because sometimes you really, really like someone

UPGRADE TO TINDER PLATINUM
Get most of Tinder’s premium features: join Tinder Platinum™ to get your likes prioritised with potential matches, send them a compliment before matching and more.

So what are you waiting for? Join millions of people worldwide! Tinder offers the most daters, increasing your chances of finding exactly what you're looking for. Download the best free dating app today!

description:
Дом с Алисой — приложение, в котором удобно настраивать умный дом и управлять им даже в дороге. Подключайте лампочки, пылесосы, датчики и тысячи других устройств — и контролируйте их здесь или через колонку.

• ВСЁ В ОДНОМ ПРИЛОЖЕНИИ
Добавляйте и удаляйте самые разные устройства, от колонок с Алисой до кондиционеров, меняйте названия и расположение — и настраивайте, как вам нравится.

• УДАЛЁННОЕ УПРАВЛЕНИЕ
Дом под контролем, даже если вы далеко: скажем, по дороге на дачу можно заранее включить обогреватель.

• ОДНА КОМАНДА ДЛЯ ВСЕГО
Запускайте нескольких устройств одной фразой — например, «Алиса, скоро буду дома». Настройте сценарий, и по этой команде включится кондиционер, пылесос начнёт уборку, а в коридоре зажжётся свет.

• ДОМ, КОТОРЫЙ САМ О ВАС ЗАБОТИТСЯ
Подключайте датчики — к примеру, температуры и влажности, — и проверяйте, как дела дома. Создайте сценарий, добавьте обогреватель и что-нибудь ещё — и дом будет сам следить, чтобы в нём хорошо дышалось.

• РУТИННЫЕ ДЕЛА ПО РАСПИСАНИЮ
Поручите часть домашних дел Алисе. Достаточно один раз настроить расписание, и она будет сама поливать цветы и включать перед сном увлажнитель.

• СЦЕНАРИЙ В ОДНО КАСАНИЕ
Добавьте сценарий в виджет — и кнопка управления будет всегда под рукой, на главном экране телефона.

• ТЫСЯЧИ РАЗНЫХ УСТРОЙСТВ
Подключайте сколько угодно домашних приборов разных производителей: в магазине вы узнаете эти устройства по отметке «Работает с Алисой».

Sajda – The Complete Islamic App, Ad-Free Since 2012  
Trusted by over 4 million Muslims around the world

Sajda is your all-in-one companion for a focused, fulfilling worship experience. Free of ads for over a decade and loved by millions globally, Sajda helps you stay spiritually connected—wherever life takes you.

Whether you're checking prayer times at work, reading the Quran while commuting, or finding the Qibla while traveling, Sajda supports your daily worship with clarity and ease.

Why millions choose Sajda:

Prayer Times  
Accurate and scholar-approved prayer timings based on your location. Fully adjustable, with countdowns to the next salah.

Adhan Alerts  
Get ready for prayer with peaceful calls from the muezzin—or choose your own sound. Includes guided rak’ah prompts.

Quran  
Read the Holy Quran with translations and transliterations. Save favorite ayahs, add personal notes, and pick your font. Effortlessly resume where you left off.

Dhikr  
Count your daily dhikr with a built-in counter. Listen to beautiful du’a recitations and join group dhikr sessions. More features are on the way, inshaAllah.

Qibla Direction  
Use the animated compass or map view (standard or satellite) to instantly find the Qibla—no matter where you are.

Widgets & Prayer Calendar  
Keep prayer times on your home screen. Share personalized salah schedules with family and friends.

Live from Makkah  
Watch real-time broadcasts from Masjid al-Haram and feel spiritually closer to the heart of Islam.

More than an app — a global movement  
Sajda has been ad-free since day one. Our mission is to connect 1 billion Muslims through simple, meaningful digital worship. Upgrade to Sajda Plus for offline Quran access, exclusive recitations, and to support prayer education worldwide.

Download Sajda now  
Join millions of Muslims from Istanbul to Jakarta, Tashkent to Barcelona. Download today and experience your faith with focus.

Breathing is one of the simplest ways to restore balance, and research shows that structured breathing practices can lower stress, improve focus, and support emotional stability. This app turns those techniques into easy daily routines that fit into real life.

On the home screen, you will see your icon, nickname, and a clear progress indicator. From here you can access breathing practices, daily tasks, your profile, app info, and settings. A statistics window lets you review your activity and see how consistent you have been.

The breathing section includes four guided methods:
• Abdominal breathing, proven to lower nervous system activity, helps reduce anxiety and return the body to a resting state.
• Rhythmic breathing balances internal pace, with short pauses after inhale and exhale that signal the body to slow down.
• Expansive breathing creates a sense of lightness by filling the chest and abdomen before releasing tension with a longer exhale.
• Releasing breath uses short inhales and extended exhales to quickly reduce irritation and emotional overload.

Each technique comes with step-by-step instructions, timing counts, and suggestions on when to use it whether before sleep, during moments of distraction, or in times of stress.

Daily tasks keep practice consistent without being repetitive. You may be asked to spend five minutes with abdominal breathing in the morning, try rhythmic cycles during a break, or combine expansive breathing with gentle stretches. At the end of the month, you can complete a “breathing session” that blends all four methods in sequence.

Your profile tracks either time or repetitions, depending on your preference. You can upload a photo, edit your nickname, and view personal analytics. Notifications, sound, and vibration can be adjusted in settings. An information section provides context on mental health and why breathing techniques are an evidence-based way to restore balance.

This is not just about exercises it is about creating a toolkit you can return to whenever you need clarity, calm, or energy. Each short session adds up, helping you build a reliable rhythm of stability throughout your day.

description:
The DMSS app can enhance your security management efficiency. You can watch real-time surveillance videos and play them back anytime, anywhere, via Wi-Fi or cellular networks. If a device alarm is triggered, DMSS will immediately push an instant notification to you.

DMSS offers：
1. Real-time Live View：
You can view real-time surveillance videos from the added devices anytime, anywhere, to help you better monitor the safety of your home environment.

2. Video Playback：
You can quickly find the events you care about by date and event category, and playback the required historical video footage.

3. Instant Alarm Notifications：
You can subscribe to different alarm events according to your needs.  When an event is triggered, you will immediately receive the message notification.

4. Device Sharing
You can share the device with family members for shared use and assign them different usage permissions.

5. Alarm Hub
You can add a variety of peripheral accessories to the alarm hub to provide warnings for potential theft, intrusion, fire, water damage, and other situations. In case of an unforeseen event, DMSS can immediately activate alarms and send out danger notifications.

6. Visual Intercom
You can add visual intercom devices to engage in video calls between the device and the DMSS, as well as perform functions like locking and unlocking.

7. Access Control
You can add access control devices to check the current status of doors and view unlock records, as well as perform remote unlocking operations on the doors.

Умный Домофон. Камеры. В одном приложении.

Домофоны:
- Вход через домофон по контуру лица. Не нужно лезть за ключами, домофон узнает вас и откроет дверь.
- Открытие двери через приложение.
- Видеозвонки на смартфон. Звонок поступает в приложение, а вы можете открыть дверь, если хотите ;)
- История звонков. Если вас не было дома, можете посмотреть, кто приходил.
- Возможность поделиться доступом с членами семьи (и не только).

Видеонаблюдение:
- Онлайн-просмотр городских и личных камер.
- Архив записей с возможностью скачать необходимый фрагмент.
- Просмотр произошедших событий, зафиксированных на камере.
- Если у вас несколько адресов, то можно привязать несколько учетных записей.
